sec.p:
The estimation F(s,t) at time t of the FES F(s) as a function of the collective variable (CV) s was determined by metadynamics (43) in its well-tempered variant (52), using the following formula:
\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
\usepackage{amsmath}
\usepackage{wasysym} 
\usepackage{amsfonts} 
\usepackage{amssymb} 
